s de los eventos. celebrados all\u00ed.\n- Escape Room \u201cAventura en el S\u00f3tano\u201d.\n- Juego de #LaCasaDelFutbol para que demuestres tu habilidad parando penaltis.\n \nAdem\u00e1s, tienes los siguientes servicios:\n- Aura, nuestro asistente virtual, para que puedas realizar determinadas gestiones utilizando la voz.\n- Metacalls, para que puedas atender las llamadas a tu tel\u00e9fono fijo desde Movistar Experiencia Inmersiva.\n \nPara cualquier duda puedes escribirnos a soporte.metaverso@telefonica.com", "short_description": "Sum\u00e9rgete desde casa en Movistar Experiencia Inmersiva y disfruta explorando, aprendiendo, jugando con tus gafas de realidad virtual."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://metaverso.telefonica.com/en/mei-legals", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Telef\u00f3nica Digital Espa\u00f1a, S.L.U", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.telefonica.com/es/sala-comunicacion/telefonica-metaverse-day/", "category": "ENTERTAINMENT", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2837265163266059", "context_category": "ENTERTAINMENT"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2676136442603296"}, {"id": "541611600222565"}, {"id": "337573230800174"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["EXPERIENCE_360_NON_GAME", "ART_CREATIVITY", "NEWS_AND_INFORMATION"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["es"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER", "MULTI_USER"], "id": "8125020050948044"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-sea1-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031359_1529212587535232_8215885608924